  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Cardio-oncology is an emerging field. Most of the data available have been issued from either
      retrospective analysis, industry data or pharmacovigilance data. These data sources include a
      number of bias.

      CONFUCIUS is a single tertiary centre prospective registry including all patients who have
      been referred for cardio-oncology assessemnt.

      The objectives are to provide a comprehensive vue of cardoi-oncology, enable to detect early
      signals of cardiotoxicity and enhance ancillary projetcts aiming at specific populations
      (e.g., type of cancer) and/or drugs.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
