    <measure>Oncology</measure>
    <time_frame>5 years</time_frame>
    <description>Adherence to oncology treatment plan as stated in the multidisciplinary team meeting in patients with cardio-oncology assessment compared to matched patients with no cardio-oncology assessment within our institution; outcomes.</description>
